text: The U.S. military arrested former coronavirus response coordinator Dr. Deborah Birx on May 26, 2021, after she allegedly conspired with the Centers for Disease Control and Prevention (CDC) to deceive the American public into believing that face masks were an effective method to mitigate the spread of Covid-19.
